STATE EX REL. HILL
v.
NAVARRE 2019-0687 Supreme Court of Ohio. July 24, 2019

CASE ANNOUNCEMENT

O'Connor, C.J., and Kennedy, French, Fischer, DeWine, Donnelly, and Stewart, JJ., concur.

MERIT DECISION WITHOUT OPINION

On respondent's motion to dismiss. Motion granted. Cause dismissed. Relator's motion for leave to amend relief requested denied.
